OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FLate sunny
OL,6,Fspells as showers clear away this
OL,7,Fevening. The rest of the night will
OL,8,Fsee mostly dry conditions, perhaps the
OL,9,Fodd light shower in the west. Patchy
OL,10,Frural frost.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSunday:FRather cloudy, especially
OL,13,Faround northern coasts where they'll
OL,14,Fbe a few showers, these perhaps
OL,15,Fspreading south in the evening. Breezy
OL,16,Fon coasts.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
